4b.poster.avif?t=1762956583\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/f99e8c955716408eb18ddf2d0865694b.webm?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205090/extras/f99e8c955716408eb18ddf2d0865694b.mp4?t=1762956583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No saves—each mistake sends you back to the start.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built-in speedrun timer and height tracker for competitive play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both helpful elements and hazards make every climb unique.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A surreal, gravity-defying world full of unpredictable challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A challenging difficulty curve that will test your perseverance.</p></li></ul>",
